title: Commission Regulation (EEC) No 694/89 of 17 March 1989 amending Annexes III and IV bis to Council Regulation (EEC) No 4136/86 with regard to certain textile products originating in the Philippines (categories 4, 5, 6, 7, 8, 15, 16, 21 and 74)
header:
COMMISSION  REGULATION (EEC) No 694/89
of 17 March 1989
amending Annexes III and IV bis to Council Regulation (EEC) No 4136/86 with regard to certain textile products originating in the Philippines (categories 4, 5, 6, 7, 8, 15, 16, 21 and 74)
THE COMMISSION OF THE EUROPEAN COMMUNITIES
main_body: Annexes III and IV bis to Regulation (EEC) No 4136/86 are hereby amended for the Philipinnes in accordance with the Annex hereto.

This Regulation shall enter into force on the day following its publication in the Official Journal of the European Communities.
It shall apply with effect from 1 January 1988.
This Regulation shall be binding in its entirety and directly applicable in all Member States.
attachments:
Done at Brussels, 17 March 1989.
For the Commission
Frans ANDRIESSEN
Vice-President
(1) OJ No L 387, 31. 12. 1986, p. 42.
(2) See page 14 of this Official Journal.
